## Core package

- **Purpose**: Durable task execution runtime with orchestration, retries, and persistence.
- **Entry point**: [durable-execution/src/index.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/index.ts)
- **Key modules**:
  - Tasks: [durable-execution/src/task.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/task.ts), [durable-execution/src/task-internal.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/task-internal.ts)
  - Storage contract: [durable-execution/src/storage.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/storage.ts)
  - Serialization: [durable-execution/src/serializer.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/serializer.ts)
  - Errors: [durable-execution/src/errors.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/errors.ts)
  - Cancellation: [durable-execution/src/cancel.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/cancel.ts)
  - Logging: [durable-execution/src/logger.ts](mdc:durable-execution/src/logger.ts)

### Quickstart

- Define tasks via `executor.task(...)` or `executor.parentTask(...)`
- Enqueue with `executor.enqueueTask`
- Start background processing: `await executor.start()`; stop with `await executor.shutdown()`
- See examples and tests: [durable-execution/tests](mdc:durable-execution/tests)

### Dev commands

- Build: `pnpm -F durable-execution build`
- Test: `pnpm -F durable-execution test`
- Type-check: `pnpm -F durable-execution type-check`
- Lint: `pnpm -F durable-execution lint`
- Format: `pnpm -F durable-execution fmt`
